  "texts": [
    "Wang et al. [209] discussed several potential applications of GAI in different layers of ISAC, with a focus on the physical layer.",
    "In addition, they investigated the problem of estimating the direction of arrival for near-field ISAC networks when the antenna spacing is greater than half the wavelength.",
    "In addition, they proposed a DFMs-based estimation algorithm by analyzing the clear and ambiguous signal spectra, which achieved an MSE of about 1.03 degrees in angle estimation.",
    "Letafati et al. [252] also discussed the potential applications of DFMs in ISAC.",
    "For example, DFMs can be used to learn the distributions of communication and sensor components by analyzing the received, noisy pilot signal."
  ],
